<h2>About</h2>
<p>
    This is a simple ASP.NET Core 8.0 application migrated from ASP.NET Framework 4.8.
</p>
<p>
    This application demonstrates migration from WebForms to Razor Pages with Azure AD authentication.
</p>
<h3>Technologies Used</h3>
<ul>
    <li>ASP.NET Core 8.0</li>
    <li>Razor Pages</li>
    <li>Azure AD (Entra ID) Authentication</li>
    <li>Azure Container Apps (Deployment Target)</li>
    <li>Application Insights</li>
    <li>Terraform (Infrastructure as Code)</li>
</ul>
